    public abstract class AbstractLinkSupportingNodeViewElementBuilder<T extends com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.elements.AbstractNodeViewElement,SELF extends com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.elements.builder.AbstractNodeViewElementBuilder<T,SELF>>
extends AbstractHtmlSupportingNodeViewElementBuilder<T,SELF>
    Base class for elements that have url properties that allow using a custom link builder function. Note that any link supporting builder also implements AbstractHtmlSupportingNodeViewElementBuilder and supports configuration of HTML escaping behaviour.

    • Method Detail

      • linkBuilder

        public SELF linkBuilder(Function<String,String> linkBuilder)
        Set a conversion function that should be applied to all url type properties when setting them as the attribute for the generated links.

        If not set, this builder will dispatch to ViewElementBuilderContext.buildLink(String). You can suppress the default behaviour by setting this property to Function.identity().

        Parameters:
        linkBuilder - to use for translating the urls
        Returns:
        current builder
